<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Were Were</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Dema dilê te xemgîn be
 Êş giran bike ser te.
 /Tu barê xwe giran meke,
 Were, were, were ba Îsa./

[V2]
 Ewê êşa te qenc bike,
 Barê giran ji ser te rake,
 /Wê canê te teze bike
 Were, were, were ba Îsa./

[V3]
 Heger Dê, bav biqewrînin,
 Xwişk, bira neyên ba te.
 Heval, hogir te bavêjin,
 Were, were, were ba Îsa

[V4]
 Ev dinya me qebul nake,
 Ji bona navê Xudan
 / Zilm û zor hatî ser me da,
 Were, were were ba Îsa./

[V5]
 Welatê me li ezmanan,
 Cinneta me li wir e,
 Êdî girîn û êş tune
 Were, were, were ba Îsa./</lyrics>
<author>Şaban Ok</author>
</song>